{"word":"G687 - ἆρα - âra - ar'-ah - Therefore","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἆρα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>âra"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>ar'-ah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Therefore"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"பொறுமையின்மை அல்லது ஆர்வம் - எதிர்மறைப் பதிலை எதிர்பார்க்கும் கேள்வி"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"marking an inferential question to which a negative answer is expected"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A form of <a href=\"#/G686 - ἄρα - ára - ar'-ah/686\">G686</a>, denoting an <i>interrogation</i> to which a negative answer is presumed: - therefore."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1944 - ἐπικατάρατος - epikatáratos - ep-ee-kat-ar'-at-os/1944\">G1944</a>, <a href=\"#/G2671 - κατάρα - katára - kat-ar'-ah/2671\">G2671</a>, <a href=\"#/G2672 - καταράομαι - kataráomai - kat-ar-ah'-om-ahee/2672\">G2672</a>, <a href=\"#/G685 - ἀρά - ará - ar-ah'/685\">G685</a>, <a href=\"#/G686 - ἄρα - ára - ar'-ah/686\">G686</a>, <a href=\"#/G687 - ἆρα - âra - ar'-ah/687\">G687</a>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}